               <msContents>
                  <summary>Faith of the Fathers, Haymanotä Abaw, ሃይማኖተ፡ አበው፡ (f<locus target="#1r"/>-67r); Five Pillars of Mystery, አምስቱ፡ አዕማደ፡ ምሥጢር፡ (f<locus target="#69r"/>-127v); Beauty of Creation, ሥነ፡ ፍጥረት። (ff. i v(erso)- vi v(erso) and 128r-133r)</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="127v" facs="007"/><title>Collection of Sayings of the Fathers</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                  <note>here called Faith of the Fathers, Haymanotä Abaw, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሃይማኖተ፡ አበው፡</foreign>, but not to be confused with the standard work by that title</note>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="1r" to="62r" facs="007"/><title>On the Incarnation</title><incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ሃይማኖተ፡ አበው፡ ርትዕት፡ ወፍኖተ፡ አምልኮ፡ ጽይሕት፡ ዘጼሕዋ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ወተለውዋ፡ ሊቃውንተ፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ነዋ፡ ናስተጋብዕ፡ ስምዓ፡ አበው፡ ዘነበቡ፡ በእንተ፡ ሃይማኖት፡ ዘሥሉስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ወበእንተ፡ ተዋሕዶተ፡ መለኮት፡ ምስለ፡ ትስብእት፡ ወበእንተ፡ ቅብዓት፡<gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                  <textLang mainLang="am" otherLangs="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz and Amharic</textLang>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="62r" to="67r" facs="068"/><title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6467Heresies">On the Heretics, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ነገረ፡ መናፍቃን፡</foreign></title><incipit xml:lang="gez">ናሁ፡ ንጽሕፍ፡ አስማቲሆሙ፡ ለመንፍቃን፡ ሰባልዮስ፡ ይቤ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩ገጽ፡ ንሕነ፡ ንቤ፡ ፫ገጽ፡ ፩ራእይ፡ ፫አካል፡ ፩አምላክ፡ ፫አስማት፡ ፩እግዚአብሔር።</incipit>
